Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥巢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一共在孵五個蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有四個孵化了  還剩下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想弄來吃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.42,0:01:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在關注啦  老師你就想著吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來客人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？沒人在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的確是在這裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖怪寫的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  這不是確實寫著的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這是只有我們才看得見的那一類東西
